   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0031-1"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb147324">Brenta-Dolomiten</rs> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb147330">Cima Tosa</rs> 3176 M) vom <rs type="place" ref="#pmb147327">M. Spinale</rs> 2021 M.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb427">Madonna di Campiglio</rs> 1553 Mtr.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb147338">Imperial Hôtel Trento</rs></hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print"><foreign xml:lang="fra">vis-à-vis de la <rs type="place" ref="#pmb147335">Gare</rs></foreign>.</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Saison Juni–September.</hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb954">Trient</rs> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb969">Südtirol</rs>)</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Même maison:</hi></hi><lb/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb147341">Grand Hôtel des Alpes</rs></hi></hi><lb/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb427">Madonna di Campiglio</rs>.</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="left" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="italics"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb147350">F. J. Oesterreicher</rs>, Prop<hi rend="superscript">re</hi></hi></hi></seg><dateline rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb427">Madonna di Campiglio</rs></hi>,</hi><lb/><date when="1904-08-31">31. Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <hi rend="pre-print">190</hi>4</date>.</dateline><salute rend="center">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Es regnet in <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb427">Campiglio</rs></hi>, und ich fahre morgen nach <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb465">Riva</rs></hi>. Von da wahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich weiter nach Ober<rs type="place" ref="#pmb40306">italien</rs>. Das Nähere hängt von meinem <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb4986">Onkel</rs> ab, der aus dem <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1061">Engadin</rs> an einen von ihm noch zu be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>timmenden Ort kommt. Im <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb58636">Gebirge</rs> werde ich Dich al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o wohl nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen können, – rathe Dir auch <pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3174_0032-1"/>dringend ab, nach
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb423 #pmb969">Tirol</rs> zu kommen, ehe das Wetter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich
               gebe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ert hat (wozu an<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinend wenig Aus<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>icht.) Aber wenn ich über <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs> zurückkehre (es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t allerdings auch möglich, daß ich <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb90751">Gotthardt</rs></hi>–<rs type="place" ref="#pmb146">Frankfurt</rs> fahre) hoffe ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr, Dir dort
               die <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03454-1"/>Hand drücken<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03454-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> kehrte über <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs> zurück. Am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1904-09-21" subtype="date-only"/> besuchte er <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs>.</note> zu können.</p><closer>Mit herzlichen Grüßen an Dich, <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> und <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb12692">Kind</rs> bin ich <lb/>Dein getreuer <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
